title: Dueling protests over gun control at Florida supermarket
text:
Dueling protests over gun control at Florida supermarket 4:28pm BST - 01:05
Survivors of a February shooting at a Florida high school were met with counter-demonstrators when they protested donations made by a supermarket chain to a gubernatorial candidate who supports gun rights. Diane Hodges reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
